(1346,	128,	'_elementor_data',	'[{\"id\":\"c8f65e4\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"flex_direction\":\"column\",\"flex_justify_content\":\"center\",\"flex_align_items\":\"center\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"3bbb3d4\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"classes\":{\"$$type\":\"classes\",\"value\":[\"e-3bbb3d4-550aa91\"]},\"tag\":{\"$$type\":\"string\",\"value\":\"h4\"},\"title\":{\"$$type\":\"html-v3\",\"value\":{\"content\":{\"$$type\":\"string\",\"value\":\"\\u0160ta je digitalna pismenost i za\\u0161to je va\\u017ena?\"},\"children\":[]}},\"link\":{\"$$type\":\"link\",\"value\":{\"isTargetBlank\":null}}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"e-heading\",\"styles\":{\"e-3bbb3d4-550aa91\":{\"id\":\"e-3bbb3d4-550aa91\",\"label\":\"local\",\"type\":\"class\",\"variants\":[{\"meta\":{\"breakpoint\":\"desktop\",\"state\":null},\"props\":{\"color\":{\"$$type\":\"color\",\"value\":\"#d52080\"}},\"custom_css\":null}]}},\"interactions\":[],\"editor_settings\":[],\"version\":\"0.0\"},{\"id\":\"0c6ac69\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>Digitalna pismenost u 21. vijeku ne predstavlja samo osnovno poznavanje rada na ra\\u010dunaru, ve\\u0107 sposobnost pronala\\u017eenja, analize, vrednovanja i bezbjednog kori\\u0161\\u0107enja informacija u digitalnom okru\\u017eenju. Ona obuhvata \\u0161irok spektar vje\\u0161tina \\u2014 od osnovne komunikacije putem elektronske po\\u0161te, preko kriti\\u010dkog prepoznavanja la\\u017enih vijesti, pa sve do naprednog upravljanja podacima i kori\\u0161\\u0107enja slo\\u017eenih softverskih alata.<\\/p><p>U savremenom informacionom dru\\u0161tvu, digitalna pismenost je postala osnovni stub konkurentnosti na tr\\u017ei\\u0161tu rada. Statistika jasno pokazuje da nedostatak ovih kompetencija direktno vodi ka socijalnoj i ekonomskoj ekskluziji, dok pojedinci sa naprednim digitalnim vje\\u0161tinama imaju drasti\\u010dno ve\\u0107e \\u0161anse za pronalazak stabilnog i dobro pla\\u0107enog posla u IKT i srodnim sektorima.<\\/p>\",\"align\":\"center\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"163dbf0\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":{\"$$type\":\"html-v3\",\"value\":{\"content\":null,\"children\":[]}},\"link\":{\"$$type\":\"link\",\"value\":{\"isTargetBlank\":null}}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"e-heading\",\"styles\":[],\"interactions\":[],\"editor_settings\":[],\"version\":\"0.0\"},{\"id\":\"418c23c\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"classes\":{\"$$type\":\"classes\",\"value\":[\"e-418c23c-6c36db9\"]},\"title\":{\"$$type\":\"html-v3\",\"value\":{\"content\":{\"$$type\":\"string\",\"value\":\"Digitalna pismenost u informacionom dru\\u0161tvu\"},\"children\":[]}},\"link\":{\"$$type\":\"link\",\"value\":{\"isTargetBlank\":null}}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"e-heading\",\"styles\":{\"e-418c23c-6c36db9\":{\"id\":\"e-418c23c-6c36db9\",\"label\":\"local\",\"type\":\"class\",\"variants\":[{\"meta\":{\"breakpoint\":\"desktop\",\"state\":null},\"props\":{\"font-family\":{\"$$type\":\"string\",\"value\":\"Arial\"},\"font-weight\":{\"$$type\":\"string\",\"value\":\"400\"},\"font-size\":{\"$$type\":\"size\",\"value\":{\"size\":24,\"unit\":\"px\"}},\"color\":{\"$$type\":\"color\",\"value\":\"#d52080\"},\"text-align\":{\"$$type\":\"string\",\"value\":\"center\"},\"background\":{\"$$type\":\"background\",\"value\":{\"color\":{\"$$type\":\"color\",\"value\":\"#ffffff\"}}}},\"custom_css\":null}]}},\"interactions\":[],\"editor_settings\":[],\"version\":\"0.0\"},{\"id\":\"3321625\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>Dobrodo\\u0161li na platformu posve\\u0107enu istra\\u017eivanju digitalnih kompetencija. <br \\/>\\u2022 Saznajte kakvo je trenutno stanje digitalne pismenosti u BiH i regionu.<br \\/>\\u2022 Pogledajte statisti\\u010dke grafikone o stopama zaposlenosti i IKT sektoru.<br \\/>\\u2022 Popunite interaktivnu anketu i odmah pogledajte rezultate glasanja u\\u017eivo<\\/p>\",\"align\":\"center\",\"_margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"40\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"e6291e3\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"text\":\"Popuni anketu\",\"link\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/digitalna-pismenost.local\\/anketa\",\"is_external\":\"\",\"nofollow\":\"\",\"custom_attributes\":\"\"},\"__globals__\":{\"background_color\":\"globals\\/colors?id=primary\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"button\"}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
